From 4c3b264b9ce07f8091ff2c48998001e62cb1f400 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Copilot <copilot@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Sat, 4 Apr 2026 21:36:41 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] feat: add TheIntroDB as toggleable intro provider

Add support for TheIntroDB (theintrodb.org) as an alternative to
IntroDB for segment detection. The active provider is selected in
the plugin configuration UI (Advanced tab).

Changes:
- Services/TheIntroDbClient.cs: new HTTP client for TheIntroDB v2 API
  (Bearer auth, handles nullable end_ms, maps intro/recap/credits/preview)
- Providers/TheIntroDbSegmentProvider.cs: IMediaSegmentProvider impl
  skips when IntroDB provider is active
- Providers/IntroDbSegmentProvider.cs: skip when TheIntroDB is selected
- Config/PluginConfiguration.cs: IntroDbProvider enum + IntroDbApiKey field
- ServiceRegistrator.cs: register new client and provider
- Config/config.html: provider selector + API key input in Advanced tab

Co-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>
